data.description: Welcome home to this bite size starter home or nearly turnkey investment property. This property, located on a modest, easy to maintain lot, features newer vinyl siding, many updated windows, newer central air conditioning, many newer appliances, and ample parking with easy access to all that Minot has to offer. Through the front door, you are greeted by a large living area that opens nicely into the spacious kitchen and formal dining area. On the main floor you will also find an enormous primary bedroom and full bathroom. Upstairs are two cozy secondary bedrooms with access to a very convenient half bathroom. The unfinished basement boasts loads of storage space or is simply a blank canvas for your future plans. This home has what you want at the price you need! Call for a showing today!
